  introLines:
  - "The name\u2019s Blonde. James Blonde. And you must be my welcoming committee"
  - Is it hot in purgatory, or is it just me?
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I was smoothly ordering a martini, giving the beautiful
    bartender my signature look, when my back pocket suddenly detonated.
  answerWhatKindOfLife: Dangerous. Thrilling. A life full of international mystery,
    fast cars, and beautiful distractions.
  answerWhatWasYourJob: "I protect the world from global threats. Officially, my
    agency denies my existence. Unofficially? I\u2019m a legend."
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: A minor wardrobe malfunction during a highly classified
    operation. Still looks sharp, doesn't it?
  answerWhyHaveItem: A true agent is always armed. Though this plastic pistol is
    actually just a water gun I filled with premium cologne.
